Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:18.87,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugi no nioi oshieru\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Hovorí mi, čo príde
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:26.05,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Boku wa tada sora wo mitsume\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Hľadím na oblohu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:33.99,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze ga hakobu hikari wo aogu\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Hľadám svetlo, čo vietor prinesie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:40.36,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano hi ienakatta kotoba tsubuyaku\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Šepkám si slová, čo som ti nemohla povedať
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:47.73,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Megutteiru dakeno mugen no sekai\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nekonečný svet ma obklopuje
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:53.97,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi no oku ni himeta shinjitsu\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}A pravda skrytá hlboko v mojich očiach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:01:01.95,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi houseki ga kagayaiteiru\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Je ako žiarivý modrý drahokam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.48,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisaku ochita shizuku\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Malá kvapka vody padá
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:12.77,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon ga shizukani hirogatteiku\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}A kruhy sa potichu šíria
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.69,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshun no katachi\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Na chvíľu dostanú tvar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:20.50,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizami yureru\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Potom zaniknú
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.46,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Posledná helikoptéra odchádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.64,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravte sa na ústup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.20,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ústup! Všetky jednotky, ústup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.58,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Čo mám robiť?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:44.85,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Choďte k západnému mólu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.79,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že nemám na výber. Pôjdem tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.00,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ústup! Pomôžte obyvateľom pri evakuácii!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.14,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,«Keel.»
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.83,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To som si mohol myslieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Godspeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo zastavte reaktor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.66,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla, hneď sa vrátim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.74,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:08.67,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.18,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Povedal si, že to nepovieš!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.51,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sľúbil si to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.88,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To bolelo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chcel som tu zostať navždy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.76,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Plače.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.05,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.43,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba sa prebudil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.11,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Neplač, lebo sa tiež rozplačem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.30,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Mešká.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.19,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:04.85,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.12,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.50,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.23,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Daj to preč. Desíš ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,On tu nie je?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.77,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,On? Nehýb sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.28,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevadí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:34.42,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz nám už pomôžeš, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.35,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti, Blantyre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.25,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabránil si roztaveniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je pobočník?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.24,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo odtiaľto vypadnime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je pobočník?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.42,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš? Rýchlo preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.08,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpovedz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.05,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je majiteľ tohto odznaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.72,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabil si ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.49,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja neviem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.99,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretol som ho, ale neviem, kam šiel potom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.42,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorím pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.76,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je zlé... Isla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.73,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To bude v poriadku, Isla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.61,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Buď ho zajali, alebo je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.65,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Viac mi povieš na lodi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.78,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nastúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nastúp?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.99,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Podrž ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:23.19,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to... H-hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.99,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pôjdeme, Isla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:29.93,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.44,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vezmite dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.70,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasadaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:57.86,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.96,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni si!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.86,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ponárame sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.75,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzdvihli sme mini-ponorku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.65,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Otočiť o 180°, kurz 2-3-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.12,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zožeňte lekára, rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.21,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Novorodenec?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.15,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.71,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno je to špión z Elektry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.41,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Špión s novorodencom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.11,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To sa mi páči.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.39,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práca, Joze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.43,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.64,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je v šoku, lebo stratila veľa krvi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.83,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...predčasnou stratou placenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.97,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale zotavuje sa rýchlo a dieťa je zdravé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.81,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíme si robiť starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.88,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz potrebuje hlavne odpočinok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.65,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.66,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieťatko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu, hneď vedľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:28.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To nesmieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomôž mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.81,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel, prosím ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.35,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je taký teplý.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.12,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Už bude dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.17,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odteraz nás čakajú len samé dobré veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.20,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To nič nie je. To nič nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.38,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že to dobre dopadlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.21,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti, Keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.35,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieťatko sa narodilo v poriadku len vďaka tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.05,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby si tam nebol, obaja by sme zomreli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.69,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.12,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Sama by som pôrod nezvládla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolelo to a myslela som, že omdliem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:30.03,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...ale jasne si spomínam, ako si zobral malého na ruky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:35.13,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...a podal mi ho so slovami: „Je to chlapec.“
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.04,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, Isla...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.74,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja aj malý ti vďačíme za život.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.35,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj ti z celého srdca ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.82,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla, to vtedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.95,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.48,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš hlad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.70,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Toho som sa bála.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:13.24,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Varovali ma, že možno nebudem mať hneď mlieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:18.08,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale potom dieťatko... zomrie od hladu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.25,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohla by som poprosiť o cukrovú vodu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:25.96,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty poď so mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.96,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán ťa chce vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.30,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.14,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je Teen, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.14,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je v prestrojení?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.95,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je našou povinnosťou niekoho zachraňovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,O tom, čo s vami bude, rozhodne kapitán.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.54,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ale jazva!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:40.89,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To muselo bolieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.11,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.95,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.32,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.81,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Som kapitán Gould.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.65,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestrite na stôl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.38,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.01,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Túto polievku som varil sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.88,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Trvalo mi tri roky, kým som dosiahol túto chuť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.32,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je? Ty nebudeš jesť?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.56,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je dobrá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.42,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Som Keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.30,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To páli!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre deti je možno trochu štipľavá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.15,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nie som žiadne decko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.48,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám štrnásť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.28,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ste si veľmi podobní.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.72,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Napokon, ste dvojčatá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:16.93,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred siedmimi rokmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:21.43,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...sme zachránili Teena pred utopením\Na priviedli sem, na Odysea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:25.93,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Odvtedy je táto ponorka Teenovým domovom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.52,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je škoda, že ste sa nestretli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.81,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako by som ho chcel stretnúť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.67,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to zradca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.05,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,On...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.78,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekvapuje ma, že máš v tvojom\Nveku také medicínske znalosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,To ty si pomáhal pri pôrode?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:54.90,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pobočník Teen sa na palube tejto\Nlode vzdelával v mnohých odboroch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.73,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátane medicíny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.91,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzeráte rovnako, ale vnútri ste úplne rozdielni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.06,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Gouldova ponorku sme stratili pri pobreží Yabitsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.22,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...okolo 20:00 včera večer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.90,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pri rýchlosti 35 uzlov...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.79,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...sa Gouldova loď musí nachádzať v tejto oblasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.66,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyšlite prieskumné helikoptéry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:06.81,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zhoďte sonarové bóje! Pripravte protiponorkové zbrane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.27,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripraviť na boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:08.97,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.43,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyšlite prieskumné helikoptéry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.58,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zhoďte sonarové bóje!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.08,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravte protiponorkové zbrane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.86,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitán Satojama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.40,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Prenasledujeme Gouldovu loď.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.40,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Blantyre sa neozval?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:41.74,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.61,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.61,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonarové bóje niečo zachytili.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.41,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to v blízkosti Hirošimy, Japonsko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.02,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže Hirošima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.52,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaženieme ho do Dhola Vira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:56.79,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dhola Vira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.68,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pošlite tri torpédoborce...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:02.20,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,...a ponorku Narušio 600 km na západ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.73,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to je tretina celej tichomorskej flotily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.39,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Obkľúčime ho a zaženieme priamo do Dhola Vira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.16,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla, to som nebol ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.93,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som nezachránil teba a dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.21,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:53.55,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:58.75,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred nami je Dhola Vira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.25,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Gould, nemáš kam ujsť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.99,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Dnešný prenos, skončený.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.80,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Koremade umaku yareta ka\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Robil som to doteraz správne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.57,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Korekara dosureba ii ka\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Čo mám teraz robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:05.45,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonna koto kangaeta koto nante nai\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nikdy som o tom nepremýšľal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.42,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoi mo yoranai koudo\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Spontánne rozhodnutia
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:11.82,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosou mo tsukanai jyokyo kamawanai\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nečakané situácie, to som ja
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.23,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorekoso sonzai shomei\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}To je môj život
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.45,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,YES, I’M DOING NOW\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Áno, som to ja
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:18.50,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tesagurinagara mo mada minu sekai wo sozo chu\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Mám svet vo svojich rukách, aj keď som ho nevidel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:19.36,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,CHECK NOW\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Tak sleduj
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:22.13,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae ga hitotsudakenaraba kase o tori harau\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Ak jediná možnosť je pretrhnúť okovy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:23.29,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,ANSWER 2\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Urob to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:24.84,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,LIMIT OFF, READY TO ROLL\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Hranice padajú, priprav sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:25.43,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,FOCUS\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Sústreď sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:26.87,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoten awase suguni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Náš cieľ je spoločný
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:27.30,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,GET ON\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nasadaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.37,0:22:31.81,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Norikoete ikeruhazu tafu kiwamari nai hibi mo\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Vznesieme sa nad ťažké nekonečné dni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:35.74,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Doshitemo tsutaetainda\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Chcem ti len povedať
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:38.05,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Je to OK, OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:40.92,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba ni kaete iko\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Poviem to slovami
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:44.72,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsudatte kono mune ni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Budeš navždy v mojom srdci
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:46.95,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,OH YEAH OH YEAH\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Áno, áno
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:50.05,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yadoru omoi tachi o\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Na tom sa nič nezmení
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:52.10,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekaiju ni hirogaru youni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Poviem to slovami, poviem to všetkým
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.16,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba ni kaete tsutaete iko\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Nech to vie celý svet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:56.20,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyoku omou imadakara koso\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Verím, že teraz je ten čas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:58.70,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba ni kaete tsutaete iko\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Povedať to slovami, povedať to všetkým
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:02.60,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyoku nari hibiku koe\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}Silným hlasom, čo sa nesie do diaľky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:07.94,TLB_OE,,0000,0000,0000,,Karenai inori to tomoni\N{\c&HFFFCFC&\3c&H2525D5&}A modlitbou, čo nikdy neumrie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:15.35,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Isla, dieťatko a ja sme skončili na\Ndivnej ponorke menom Odyseus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.52,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to nie je všetko. Pred nami\Nje obrovský podmorský vír!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:19.92,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nás zachytí, je s nami koniec!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:23.29,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Tide-Line Blue\N~Dhola Vira~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:24.56,TLB,,0000,0000,0000,,Tešte sa.
